extends layout

block content
  .static-page
    .static-card
      span.static-eyebrow Support
      h1 Support Center
      p Need help with your account, posts, comments, or community features? This page explains how to get support and solve common problems.

      .static-grid
        .static-info-box
          h3 Account Help
          p If you cannot access your profile, make sure you are logged in with the correct account. If you do not have an account, create one to unlock posting, commenting, liking, and rating features.

        .static-info-box
          h3 Posting Help
          p If your post is not appearing, check that the title, category, and content fields are completed. Make sure image and video links are valid and accessible.

        .static-info-box
          h3 Community Safety
          p If you see inappropriate comments or harmful behavior, use the report feature where available. Reports help administrators review issues and keep the community safe.

      .static-section
        h2 Common Issues

      .static-section
        h2 I cannot create a post
        p You must be logged in to create a post. Go to the login page, sign in, then use the Create Post button in the navigation bar.

      .static-section
        h2 My image or video does not show
        p Check that the image or video URL is correct. For videos, use a valid embeddable link when possible. Some websites may block external embedding.

      .static-section
        h2 My comments are not showing
        p Make sure your comment is not empty and that you are logged in. Refresh the post page after submitting. If the issue continues, contact the site administrator.

      .static-section
        h2 Likes, ratings, or views are not updating
        p Refresh the page after interacting with a post. If numbers still do not update, the website may need a database or route check by the administrator.

      .static-section
        h2 Reporting Content
        p Use the report button on comments that break community standards. Reports should be used for spam, harassment, offensive content, abuse, or other harmful behavior.

      .static-section
        h2 Community Guidelines
        p Be respectful, stay on topic, avoid spam, give credit where appropriate, and do not post content that violates the rights of others. Gaming Community is built for helpful and friendly discussion.

      .static-section
        h2 Contact Support
        p For account issues, technical problems, moderation requests, or privacy questions, contact the Gaming Community administrator. Include your username, the page where the issue happened, and a clear explanation of the problem.

      .static-section
        h2 Suggested Support Details
        p When asking for help, include the problem, your username, the post title or page link, what you expected to happen, and what actually happened. This helps support resolve the issue faster.

      .static-actions
        a.static-btn(href="/posts") Go to Posts
        a.static-btn.secondary(href="/profile") My Profile